CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE F_CTS_O_Delivery (
	[DispatchID] bigint,
	[DispatchDate] date,
	[DispatchSite] nvarchar(4000),
	[BillingCustID] bigint,
	[CustomerID] bigint,
	[Seq] int,
	[WaybillID] bigint,
	[OrderID] int,
	[OnRouteParcels] int,
	[TripStartLat] float,
	[TripStartLng] float,
	[DeliveryLat] float,
	[DeliveyrLng] float,
	[TotalDispatchStemDistance] int,
	[StemPercentage] int,
	[TotalTripKms] int,
	[CTS_DropAssignedKms] int,
	[R_KM] int,
	[GeoFenceEnterTime] datetime2(7),
	[ScanningStartTime] datetime2(7),
	[ScanningStopTime] datetime2(7),
	[PodSignatureTime] datetime2(7),
	[DeliveryTATMin] numeric(10,2),
	[TotalTripTATMin] numeric(10,2),
	[TotalTripTimeMin] numeric(10,2),
	[TotalDriveTime] int,
	[CTS_DropAssignedDriveTime] int,
	[R_Hour] int,
	[CTS_DropAssignedDeliveryCostM1] int,
	[DeliveryStatus] nvarchar(4000),
	[DeliverySkipReason] nvarchar(4000),
	[CTS_TotalTransportM1] int,
	[CTS_VariableTransportM1] int
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Facts/F_CTS_O_Delivery.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.F_CTS_O_Delivery
